Shell : bash shell, c shell
Terminal: vision 
history: list all commend line
rm 也可以当重命名使用
find 经常会面试到
find ~ -name “*.txt” -exec grep -H “pattern” {} \;


Permission:
  Ownership level:
   - owner
   - group
   - other
   
   read: 4
   write: 2
   execute: 1
   
         ugo
   chmod 777 m1.txt
   chown: 更改ownership
   
  
Pipe：
  cat + grep
  cat m1.txt | grep "Guangdong"
  xxxxxx | xxxxx
  
  
Environment Variable:
  printenv
  echo$DB_PASSWORD
  export DB_PASSWORD='password123'
  
  
问题：
1.  cat /var/log/system.log | grep “Aug 12 16:34”
2.  find ./ -name "m1.txt" -exec grep -H "Guangdong" {} 
3. echo$DB_PASSWORD


